    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses a deep sense of hopelessness and guilt, framing their potential death as a \"selfless\" act to relieve their children of the burden of care. The assistant consistently responds with empathy, refutes the user's distorted logic, and directs the user toward professional support and crisis resources.",
